{"tid":825716,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【一入豪門深似海】曾與古天樂合演家有囍事2009 愛情治療師曹迪克女神小敏跳樓自殺","createTime":"2018-09-17T17:47:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T09:38:56.000Z","uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b946ea633e6161092c0ad5279ffb3d6d100712c0","tid":825716,"uid":204717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=f&amp;nid=210784 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Df%26nid%3D210784%20&d=zQoJ4cj6a907DmgiJWQO%2BfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=0ed9d2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Df%26nid%3D210784%20&h=039f2f81\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=f&amp;nid=210784 </a><br />\n<br />\n曾與古天樂合演電影《家有囍事2009》的內地女星沈麗君，在本月10日墮樓自殺身亡，所屬公司已證實死訊，終年35歲。她早年嫁入豪門後育有一對子女，有指她一直忍受老公出軌，甚至遭小三騷擾，加上患子宮頸癌末期，令沈麗君走上絕路。 <br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒流出沈麗君遺書的文件檔，提及老公精子畸形率高加上她身子弱，佗第2胎時險流產，更打了200多枝安胎針，懷孕期間又發現老公和小三同居，完全不關心她。遺書中講及「我現在很後悔，為甚麼不在那時候決然離婚，孩子還在哺乳期肯定會判給我，就不會有今天的悲劇了，這是我此生最後悔的事。」最後一句寫下：「自己選的路，如今卻讓我走投無路。」 <br />\n<br />\n沈麗君最後一則微博帖文在上月18日發出，不少網民在帖文留言，悼念沈麗君，「一路走好我們的小兔子」、「願你此以後只有快樂」、「剛聽到這個噩耗，怎麼也不敢相信，久久不能平復心情！親愛的一路走好！」"},{"pid":"2bb7690468d719d5d871712eed7daf3a9faf7cc6","tid":825716,"uid":204717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T17:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photocdn.sohu.com/20090120/Img261862000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotocdn.sohu.com%2F20090120%2FImg261862000.jpg&h=5d5a5c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1872390/org/b1c701a8377dbaae40d789a2698dcc7a.jpg/GOl7PUaxp87ErHtyI8JykXj1OGMOk86GznUzbc51M20?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1872390%2Forg%2Fb1c701a8377dbaae40d789a2698dcc7a.jpg%2FGOl7PUaxp87E